body:
### Welcome to admob for flash.
admob for flash is a free ane lib for flash developer.it enable flash mobile application load admob advertising. it is easy to use.

user can show all type of banner ad and full screen(interstitial advertising) ad of admob
user can show landscope and portrait advertising in actionscript 3 mobile application
user can set postion of ad

### Requirements 
flash air sdk 3.1 or higher,

iPhone or iPad devices

Recommend flash builder 4.7 

### mark
this lib do not work on pc and Simulator，but well on device

###download

verion base on admob ios sdk 6.2
https://github.com/lilili87222/admob-for-flash/blob/master/admob%20for%20flash%20ios/admobapp/anes/admob.ane

if you get a adspport error please download this version
 https://github.com/lilili87222/admob-for-flash/raw/a54a6bec82f65e78635a501531c599e7d70f166d/admob%20for%20flash%20ios/admobapp/anes/admob.ane

### useage
ref://https://developers.google.com/mobile-ads-sdk/docs/admob/intermediate
ref://https://developers.google.com/mobile-ads-sdk/docs/admob/smart-banners
```
var ad:Admob=Admob.getInstance();
 if(ad.isSupported){
   ad.setUnitId(gid);
   ad.setAdType(AdType.kGADAdSizeBanner);
   ad.setPosition(0,100);
   ad.setIsLandscape(true);
   ad.addToDisplayList();
   ad.refresh();
 }else{
   trace("not support");
 }
```

### useage  detail
```
package
{
	import flash.display.Sprite;
	import so.cuo.anes.admob.AdType;
	import so.cuo.anes.admob.Admob;
	[SWF(width="640", height="960", frameRate="60", backgroundColor="#cccccc")]
	public class AdmobTestSimple extends Sprite
	{
	//a14fde93a405e01  is   admob    app id，login to www.admob.com for more info
		private var gid:String="a14fde93a405e01";
		public function AdmobTestSimple()
		{
			super();
			//create admob instance 
			var ad:Admob=Admob.getInstance();
			//test if this lib work on current runtime
			if(ad.isSupported){
			//set google admob id
				ad.setUnitId(gid);
				//set size of admob,please ref tohttps://developers.google.com/mobile-ads-sdk/docs/admob/intermediate for more info about size
				ad.setAdType(AdType.kGADAdSizeBanner);
				//set the position of ad view.
				ad.setPosition(0,100);
				//set if show ad landscape,if true,ad will show as landscape mode
				ad.setIsLandscape(true);
				//add to displayobject tree ,just as sprite.addChild(displayObject)
				ad.addToDisplayList();
				//load ad
				ad.refresh();
			}else{
				trace("not support");
			}
		}
	}
}
```
